text: Hey Ahmed! This is a Slack for HubSpot developers. If you have any services you wish to provide, please post in <#CBNDYJJAZ|jobs> - self promotion is not permitted elsewhere
Hello :wave:  is the approvals system planned to be released for custom approvals not the ones defined there?

Hi!
When i list my forms, i can see the number of page where i use it, but in some cases the form say that i use it in a page where it doesn't exist.

What is it possible?

Thanks!

I can’t say for certain, but I would guess that this is related to consent management settings? The cookie banner has the ability to automatically detect and block any scripts or content that would add a cookie before consent is provided.

I’d take a peek in at the settings for your cookie banner and consent management and see if someone’s enabled automatic blocking.
